Usage: placePipeline [-help] [-netGroup <netGroupNames>]
                     [-status {softFixed placed fixed}] [-timingBased] [{-region } [-utilization <val>]]

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-netGroup <netGroupNames>            # name(s) of net group(s)
                                     # (string, optional)
-region                              # create regions for flops
                                     # (bool, optional)
-status {softFixed placed fixed}     # placement status of flops
                                     # (enum, optional)
-timingBased                         # automatically find reserve lengths
                                     # (bool, optional)
-utilization <val>                   # expected utilization of regions for
                                     # flops (float, optional, min=0, max=1)